\startbuffer
\startformula
 \check{u} + \widecheck{u} + \widecheck{uv} + \widecheck{uvw}
 \breakhere
 + \widecheck{uvwx} + \widecheck{abcdefghijklmn...}
 \breakhere
 \hat{u} + \widehat{u} + \widehat{uv} + \widehat{uvw}
 + \widehat{uvwx} + \widehat{abcdefghijklmn...}
 \breakhere
 \tilde{u} + \widetilde{u} + \widetilde{uv} + \widetilde{uvw}
 \breakhere
 + \widetilde{uvwx} + \widetilde{abcdefghijklmn...}
\stopformula
\stopbuffer

\typebuffer

\getbuffer

The collection of extensible arrows/stackers hereunder can be placed on top of an
expression of there under. Replacing the \type{\over...} part with \type{\under
...} the arrow will be placed under the expression.

\stopsubsection

